      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:14:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度监管机构寻求限制外国 ETF 的新资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-regulator-seeks-to-limit-fresh-flows-into-foreign-etfs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度市场监管机构已要求当地基金管理公司停止接受投资海外交易所交易基金产品的新认购，因为此类投资的价值已接近全行业的上限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-regulator-seeks-to-limit-fresh-flows-into-foreign-etfs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:12:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
