    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市有望实现 2012 年以来最长涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/european-stocks-on-track-for-longest-winning-run-since-2012</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五基本持平，守住历史高位，并有望连续第九周上涨，这是自 2012 年以来最长的连续上涨，原因是人们对经济的信心不断增强，而且降息即将到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/european-stocks-on-track-for-longest-winning-run-since-2012</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:23:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
